      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">四牡.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>四牡騑騑，周道倭遲。豈不懷歸？王事靡盬，我心傷悲。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>My four steeds advanced without stopping;
The way from Zhou was winding and tedious.
Did I not have the wish to return?
But the king's business was not to be slackly performed;
And my heart was wounded with sadness.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-luming-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
