      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·002.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">四牡.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>四牡騑騑，嘽嘽駱馬。豈不懷歸？王事靡盬，不遑啟處。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>My four steeds advanced without stopping;
They panted and snorted, the white steeds black-maned.
Did I not have the wish to return?
But the king's business was not to be slackly performed;
And I had not leisure to kneel or to sit.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-luming-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
