      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·002.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">四牡.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>翩翩者鵻，載飛載下，集于苞栩。王事靡盬，不遑將父。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Filial doves keep flying about,
Now soaring aloft, and now descending,
Collecting on the bushy oaks;
But the king's business was not to be slackly performed;
And I had not leisure to nourish my father.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
