      <prop type="x-translation-ref">四牡.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>翩翩者鵻，載飛載止，集于苞杞。王事靡盬，不遑將母。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Filial doves keep flying about,
Now flying, now stopping,
Collecting on the bushy medlars;
But the king's business was not to be slackly performed;
And I had not leisure to nourish my mother.</seg>
      </tuv>
