      <prop type="x-translation-ref">四牡.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>駕彼四駱，載驟駸駸。豈不懷歸？是用作歌，將母來諗。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I yoked my four white steeds, black-maned;
They hurried away with speed.
But did I not wish to return?
Therefore I make this song,
Announcing my wish to nourish my mother.</seg>
      </tuv>
